Plus One Admission 2026 – 2027

Dear Parents and Students,

Greetings from Holy Angels!

We hope and pray that all our SSLC students will achieve excellent results in the SSLC Examination 2026.

We are happy to inform you that Plus One Admissions for the Academic Year 2026 – 2027 will commence immediately on the very day and hour of the SSLC Results announcement.

Parents and students are requested to come prepared with the following documents:

Documents Required -

Duly filled-in Application Form
Mark Sheet
Xerox Copy of Aadhaar Card
Birth Certificate Copy
Community Certificate Copy
Family Card Copy
Any other relevant documents

Important Instructions -

Students are advised to choose the Group and Language wisely based on their marks, aptitude, and interests.

Admission will be granted based on eligibility and availability of seats.

Fee Details -

School Fee (through DD/ GPay) – Rs. 46,350/-

Uniform Amount (Cash Only) – Rs. 6,950/-

Diary, SSM, ID Card &amp; Miscellaneous Charges (Cash Only) – Rs. 800/-

French Fee (Optional) – Rs. 5,000/-

Note:
Admission will be confirmed only after the full payment of the above-mentioned amount at the time of admission.

No claim for admission will be entertained without completion of payment during admission.

We are proud to share that Holy Angels has achieved a remarkable Plus Two Result in 2026, securing the Second Rank in the State with the top score of 597 marks and Result 💯%.

We are also delighted to inform you that a good number of CBSE students have already enrolled in the Plus One Batch 2026 – 2027 immediately after their board results.

We welcome all aspiring students to become part of the Holy Angels family and continue the tradition of academic excellence.

Wishing you all grand success and a bright future!

Principal‬" data-testid="last-msg-status"><span dir="ltr" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">HOLY ANGELS’ MATRIC HR. SEC. SCHOOL
Plus One Admission 2026 – 2027

Dear Parents and Students,

Greetings from Holy Angels!

We hope and pray that all our SSLC students will achieve excellent results in the SSLC Examination 2026.

We are happy to inform you that Plus One Admissions for the Academic Year 2026 – 2027 will commence immediately on the very day and hour of the SSLC Results announcement.

Parents and students are requested to come prepared with the following documents:

Documents Required -

Duly filled-in Application Form
Mark Sheet
Xerox Copy of Aadhaar Card
Birth Certificate Copy
Community Certificate Copy
Family Card Copy
Any other relevant documents

Important Instructions -

Students are advised to choose the Group and Language wisely based on their marks, aptitude, and interests.

Admission will be granted based on eligibility and availability of seats.

Fee Details -

School Fee (through DD/ GPay) – Rs. 46,350/-

Uniform Amount (Cash Only) – Rs. 6,950/-

Diary, SSM, ID Card &amp; Miscellaneous Charges (Cash Only) – Rs. 800/-

French Fee (Optional) – Rs. 5,000/-

Note:
Admission will be confirmed only after the full payment of the above-mentioned amount at the time of admission.

No claim for admission will be entertained without completion of payment during admission.

We are proud to share that Holy Angels has achieved a remarkable Plus Two Result in 2026, securing the Second Rank in the State with the top score of 597 marks and Result <img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="💯" draggable="false" class="b72 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -60px -40px;">%.

We are also delighted to inform you that a good number of CBSE students have already enrolled in the Plus One Batch 2026 – 2027 immediately after their board results.

We welcome all aspiring students to become part of the Holy Angels family and continue the tradition of academic excellence.

Wishing you all grand success and a bright future!

