Schedule 8th to 11th May 

Somnath-Virasat ke 75 Saal. Somnath is a symbol of India&#39;s indomitable civilisation. 75 years ago, the resolve of the Iron Man Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, paved the way for the modern revival of Somnath. Today, under the leadership of Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi, this sacred land proudly heralds India&#39;s cultural renaissance.

